吃，并将剩菜重新加热至酥脆完美。我们建议您查看我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-air-fryers-133047180.html">空气炸锅指南，</a>如果您想给他们一些更大的东西，可以一次煮更多的食物——但如果您只是在寻找您的毕业生以及他们的伴侣或最喜欢的室友，Instant Vortex Mini 将喂饱他们。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/best-gifts-for-grads-under-50-114506320.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-gifts-for-grads-under-50-114506320.html?src=rss]]><source_id>engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4b0ad802-0aea-3ee4-bec9-01600d2a2985</guid><dc:creator>瓦伦蒂娜·帕拉迪诺</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 15 Jun 2023 16:49:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686847770</ingested><modified> 2023-06-15T16:49:39+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[firetvstick4k]]></category><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[anker]]></category><category><![CDATA[entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[M720Triathlon]]></category><category><![CDATA[thebuyersguide]]></category><category><![CDATA[dadsandgrads2020]]></category><category><![CDATA[tribit]]></category><category><![CDATA[commerce]]></category><category><![CDATA[echoflex]]></category><category><![CDATA[XSoundGo]]></category><category><![CDATA[RAVPower]]></category><category><![CDATA[powerline]]></category><category><![CDATA[Logitech]]></category><category><![CDATA[Amazon]]></category><category><![CDATA[gear]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicEquipment,Instruments&Components]]></category><category><![CDATA[Entertainment(general)]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts&Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[ElectronicsAccessories]]></category><category><![CDATA[OfficeElectronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology&Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Lifestyle]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![C